 
<p>

A Chicago thug <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2022/07/21/us/chicago-13-year-old-paralyzed-police/index.html">shot a teenager</a> who ran away, as he was putting his hands up
while holding a camera phone. The boy is now paralyzed.
<p>
California thugs <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2022/07/20/us/rob-adams-san-bernardino-police-shooting/index.html">killed a man</a> who ran away with a phone in his hand.

 